<l>vaḵkāṉ meykeṭac cuṭṭumuta laimmu</l>
<l>ṉaḵkā ṉiṟṟa lākiya paṇpē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>After the words in <foreign xml:lang="ta">-ai</foreign> which begin with the demonstrative</l>
<l>[vowels] it is the usage to drop the consonant <foreign xml:lang="ta">v</foreign></l>
<l>[of vaṟṟu] and let the <foreign xml:lang="ta">a</foreign> remain.<note place="foot">E.g. <foreign xml:lang="ta">avai + vaṟṟu + ai &gt; avaṟṟai.</foreign></note></l>
      </lg>
